data.title: FIFA 23 All Leagues and Clubs List
data.meta_description: See the full list of playable clubs and leagues in EA SPORTS FIFA 23.
data.text:
FIFA 23 brings you The World’s Game with unrivalled authenticity, featuring football’s biggest stars, leagues, and teams.

Plus, new in FIFA 23 is the addition of Women’s Club Football, allowing you to play as the biggest stars of the women’s game across the Barclays WSL and Division 1 Arkema.

With more than 19,000 players across 700 teams, in more than 100 stadiums and over 30 leagues around the world, FIFA 23 is the place you can play in iconic competitions such as the UEFA Champions League, UEFA Europa League, UEFA Europa Conference League, Premier League, Bundesliga, LaLiga Santander, CONMEBOL Libertadores and CONMEBOL Sudamericana.

See the full list of leagues and clubs in FIFA 23 below.

** Teams have generic kits and crests, but authentic players unless otherwise noted.

*** Only on PlayStation® 5, PlayStation® 4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, PC via Origin™ and Steam, and Stadia.

FIFA 23 launches September 30, 2022 on PlayStation ®5, Xbox Series X|S, PC, Stadia, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One. Pre-order* now!

Follow @EASPORTSFIFA on Twitter, Instagram, and YouTube for all the latest news and updates.
